---

<section class="py-24 bg-charcoal-900">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-white mb-8">
      Most businesses rely on multiple tools:
    </h2>

    <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-10">
      {[
        { name: 'Websites', icon: 'M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9' },
        { name: 'Email', icon: 'M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z' },
        { name: 'Forms', icon: 'M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z' },
        { name: 'Messaging', icon: 'M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z' }
      ].map((item) => (
        <li class="bg-charcoal-800 border border-charcoal-600/50 rounded-lg px-5 py-5 text-center">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-500 mx-auto mb-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d={item.icon} />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-gray-300">{item.name}</span>
        </li>
      ))}
    </ul>

    <p class="text-xl text-gray-400">
      These tools often operate independently, without proper integration.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
